issue.title: IISNode server deployment
issue.body: Lots of changes to the file structure. The backend has been moved to another repo: https://github.com/joeySchentrup/receipt-less-backend. This is only the frontend. It may not longer work locally due to the changes but works on azure: https://receipt-less.azurewebsites.net/. Any further changes to the master branch will automatically up the website at the above address. The backend is not running right now but will when the internet at my apt is fixed.
